name: Saikyou Ginsei Gomoku Narabe
overview: ■ Game with 5 characters You can enjoy from beginners to advanced users with a wide range of strength from Level 1 to Level 5. Five characters of personality race play the opponent of the player. ■ Game record preservation function It is possible to store up to 10 game data. You can save game records for breaks in the middle of the game and for game research. ■ Enhanced functions Beginners also have a safe hint function. Equipped with abundant functions for enjoying opponents such as game playing function which can also be used for research.
